# A simple project to show hypercore working on mobile

This project has multiple branches, each working towards demonstrating hypercore on mobile using a different build system.

Commands:
- `$ yarn setup`
  Initialize the repo
- `$ yarn start`
  Launch development server and configure ip & port (leave running)
- `$ yarn build-android`
  Create an apk
- `$ yarn run-android`
  Launch on connected device
- `$ yarn build-ios`
  TODO: build for iphone once I get a mac
- `$ yarn run-ios`
  TODO: launch on connected iphone once I get a mac
